title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Apr 25 2022

description:
CNN gets its hands on Mark Meadows' text messages - it's just another smear of Trump and Trumpers. Sen. Rand Paul (R-KY) talks about the end of the mask mandate. Dr. Mehmet Oz talks about the Trump endorsement in the Pennsylvania Senate race. Twitter accepts Elon Musk's offer.
